        <h2>
            胡塞尔思想的发展的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6268022">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6268022/" class="title-link">清楚詳實的好書</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6268022"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/65629425/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65629425/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">aeqwong123</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-08"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-08 12:21:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6268022_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  這是對於西方哲學有基本了解的讀者（即是說起碼懂得理性主義與經驗主義之爭，康德革命之處）入門現象學的好書。  作者由胡塞爾在《邏輯研究》時的現象學思想慢慢解釋他發現此在此時學說發現甚麼問題，從而向先驗現象學轉向。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6268022_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6268022_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










